T6040 J614s ANS/NVMe controlled probe -- 2026-07-13

Safety result
-------------
No namespace appeared. No identify, partition, mount, repair, format, flush,
filesystem, or other storage command was issued. The fatal boundary remained
before CoastGuard, SART-entry, mailbox, and NVMe command traffic.

